{"thag1.20:0.1":"Theragatha 1.20 ","thag1.20:0.2":"Ekakanipata ","thag1.20:0.3":"Dutiyavagga ","thag1.20:0.4":"Ajitattheragatha ","thag1.20:1.1":"“Marane me bhayam natthi, ","thag1.20:1.2":"nikanti natthi jivite; ","thag1.20:1.3":"Sandeham nikkhipissami, ","thag1.20:1.4":"sampajano patissato”ti. ","thag1.20:1.5":"… Ajito thero … ","thag1.20:1.6":"vaggo dutiyo. ","thag1.20:2.0":"Tassuddanam ","thag1.20:2.1":"Culavaccho mahavaccho, ","thag1.20:2.2":"vanavaccho ca sivako; ","thag1.20:2.3":"Kundadhano ca belatthi, ","thag1.20:2.4":"dasako ca tatopari; ","thag1.20:2.5":"Singalapitiko thero, ","thag1.20:2.6":"kulo ca ajito dasati. "}